NCDHC Audit Subtype

http://hl7.org.au/fhir/ch/v1/ValueSet/ncdhc-audit-subtype-1

National Children's Digital Health Collaborative - Audit Subtype which recorded to capture the category of the event. In this instance the specific Health Interaction name will be derived.
